  m_Text: This shows you how to make objects that can be selected when you tap on
    them. This is done by first adding the <color=#0FF>LeanSelectableByFinger</color>
    component to them. You can then make a new GameObject with the <color=#0FF>LeanFingerTap</color>
    and <color=#0FF>LeanSelectByFinger</color> components, and connect the <color=#0FF>LeanFignerTap</color>
    component's <color=#0FF>OnFinger</color> event to the <color=#0FF>LeanSelectByFinger.SelectScreenPosition</color>
    function.
